data.description: ***PRICE HAS BEEN LOWERED AGAIN!!!*** ONE STORY home on a .25 acre CORNER LOT in established neighborhood in Seguin. Open kitchen with granite counters, updated lighting, wood laminate flooring, & spacious eating area. Large living room! Bedrooms all have ceiling fans and nice sized closets. Covered patio is partially "enclosed." Big back yard is ready for you to add a pool, install a garden, or simply leave it as a GREAT SPACE for kids and/or pets to play. ROOF REPLACED in Aug. 2023, EXTERIOR PAINTED & GUTTERS installed 2020, WINDOWS REPLACED 2019, back privacy fence installed 2019. Location allows for quick easy access to I-10! SELLING AS-IS BECAUSE SELLERS WILL BE MOVED OUT OF STATE IN LESS THAN A WEEK.
